dct_title_s: Map of the North Western Frontier of India, showing the Pamir region and part of Afghanistan
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading and spot heights. "London, Stanford's Geographical Establishment."--Lower right margin. Map shows boundary of Afghanistan as assumed in the Anglo Russian agreement of 1872-3, Russia's administrative boundary, and British political frontiers. Dr. Lansdell's route indicated in red.
